OL,3,CMan denies manslaughter over death of
OL,4,Cbus driver assaulted on bridge
OL,6,FA man has denied manslaughter in
OL,7,Fconnection with the death of a bus
OL,8,Fdriver following an assault on
OL,9,FBattersea Bridge in London.
OL,11,FGary Jones, 32, appeared at Kingston
OL,12,FCrown Court via a video-link from HMP
OL,13,FWandsworth on Monday charged over the
OL,14,Fdeath of Sergei Krajev.
OL,16,FThe defendant spoke only to confirm
OL,17,Fhis name and enter a not guilty plea
OL,18,Fto a single count of manslaughter.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
