OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781695157
OL,3,CMan denies manslaughter over death of
OL,4,Cbus driver assaulted on bridge
OL,6,FMr Krajev was assaulted following a
OL,7,Fconfrontation on the pavement while
OL,8,Fhis bus was parked at a stop shortly
OL,9,Fbefore 12.30am on May 18, the
OL,10,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,12,FThe 64-year-old was taken to hospital
OL,13,Fby London's Air Ambulance but died the
OL,14,Fnext day.
OL,16,FJones was arrested on the day of the
OL,17,Fincident on suspicion of causing
OL,18,Fgrievous bodily harm and later charged
OL,19,Fwith the offence.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/3
