CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781695157
OL,3,CMan denies manslaughter over death of
OL,4,Cbus driver assaulted on bridge
OL,6,FThis was replaced with a charge of
OL,7,Fmanslaughter after Mr Krajev died,
OL,8,Fprosecutor Nathan Rasiah KC told the
OL,9,Fcourt on Monday.
OL,11,FA trial date was fixed for April 12
OL,12,Fnext year at Kingston Crown Court.
OL,14,FIt is expected to last for 10 days.
OL,16,FJones, of no fixed address, was
OL,17,Fgranted conditional bail until then.
